					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Will your game have a map like the one in <em>Super Metroid</em> or <em>Castlevania: SOTN</em>? That might be useful depending on how big the game world is.
<br />
<br />Lack of a map is one of the major reasons I dislike the NES version of <em>Metroid</em>. The rooms are so similar to each other, it's really hard to tell them apart. Getting lost is a great way to frustrate the player, so I'd recommend preventing that in any way possible.</div>

